user.biography:
The Official Instagram of Alfa Romeo USA.
Powering passion since 1910.
Tag your best shots with #MyAlfa to be featured amongst our finest.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Alfa Romeo USA on August 16, 2021. May be an image of car and outdoors.

node.text:
If we had to describe our #MontereyCarWeek in three words, they would be: over too soon. Here are just a few of our favorite moments and motors from this year’s events. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

node.text:
You don’t go all the way to #MontereyCarWeek to just look at vehicles. That’s why we’ve been hosting Ride and Drives around the picturesque @FolktaleWinery, giving hungry Alfisti a taste of our Italian, turbocharged delicacies. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

node.text:
#MontereyCarWeek has arrived and so have we. There were nothing but automotive stunners in attendance yesterday at Concours on the Avenue, our Giulia Quadrifoglio and Stelvio Quadrifoglio a fine pair amongst them. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
